RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 1M 70Y All Weather Track CR: 73. Maiden Claiming Purse 21000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Claiming Price $16,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: STORM BRAVE pulled while up close around the five path into the backstretch, advanced to take command while confidently handled in the three path midway around the far turn, opened up while tipping slightly inwards into the lane, was much the best and driven out. HOLIDAY FANTASY settled in range around the two path, lost ground and was under a ride going into the far turn, angled out to the seven path passing the eighth pole, and kept on between foes to place. CHACHARERO rated along the rail, was in tight between foes early around the far turn, fanned out to the eight path into the stretch, and ran on for show. NETWORKING bumped with an inner foe at the start, tracked in the four path, received right handed urging from the three path rounding the far turn, went back out to the four path entering the lane, but finished evenly. DONTONIO bumped with an outer foe at the start, trailed in the three path, circled inner foes in the four path around the far turn, swung out to the six path into the lane, but flattened late. ADIOS YOUR HONOR set the pace in the two path, but was overtaken while along the inside midway around the far turn, and faded in the stretch. GALACTIC JACK prompted the pace in the three path but gaveway early around the far turn.
